{"tid":2405300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"瓏門盤菜全線無曬龍蝦","createTime":"2021-02-12T08:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T14:06:10.000Z","uid":56717,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08e3e87e2df8ac3400d779edd3dea77d03054773","tid":2405300,"uid":56717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"訂左六人盤菜連兩隻龍蝦<br />\n見琴日幾間都出曬事攪到勁樣衰<br />\n特登早少少四點去拎<br />\n都已經話全線無曬龍蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢一隻龍蝦肯換番一罐鮑魚+一底糕比我<br />\n收貨算數但其實心底想食龍蝦多d<br />\n另外，暫時見拎盤菜等幾分鐘就拎得<br />\n<br />\n利申：未開飯未有食評住，不過望落唔錯"},{"pid":"a71074008a7a8da7e03aac238c57ea3db601ca76","tid":2405300,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"新年食龍蝦好唔老黎，龍門好波"},{"pid":"da39e04fbb6b6f63caf4bec9a8daaebb7735667b","tid":2405300,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7a2dd845abfd690eb222cb7c2c4056b2efa010","tid":2405300,"uid":56717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"少少失望<br />\n不過其實個味應該唔夾嘅<br />\n多兩罐鮑魚都好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5e80b228e9eed30c76241fdf24af5747c6ee98","tid":2405300,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"唔計啦"},{"pid":"c6da8564804e8f695a2ba8a6352c03cac7735f8e","tid":2405300,"uid":79507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"支持左龍門咁耐第一次失望<br />\n屋企人期待食龍蝦 而家話冇哂"},{"pid":"d247c6cd43fc64cd650a25994ef58b4623160b83","tid":2405300,"uid":56717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"食完<br />\n味道就唔錯，份量都好夠<br />\n但料真係唔特別靚<br />\n平番1/3 就合理喇<